snippet: A woman who was critically wounded in the Santa Monica shooting spree died Sunday, bringing the number of the gunman’s victims to five.
abstract: California woman who was critically wounded in Santa Monica shooting spree, dies at UCLA Medical Center, bringing number of gunman's victims to five.
